\fs26 \cf0 Public persona is carefully crafted. Enjoys celebrity status. But Birakay is a serious musician.  A defender of and advocate for bards, players, actors and poets despite constraints of Helioptic culture and law. Spends time working on writing and composing fresh material for popular consumption, while other works remain hidden or performed only outside of the Helioptic provinces. In public he is outgoing, brash, and flirts with everyone.  In person he is kind and considerate, abhors violence and prejudice. Romatically is exclusively gay. Believes that radical social changes are needed in the Saskan Lands. Would like to see the old rivalries ended. Is worried about survival.
