\fs26 \cf0 Has not overcome his Helioptic ideological training.  Has anxieties that his male expression and his embrace of new songs will contribute to the Re-emergence of the Catastrophe.  Is drawn towards resistance forces amongst the Settany and the Kahila, the star-gazers and so on, particularly when they offer alternative views on gender expression and new music. 
