\fs26 \
Travels a lot. Is famous everywhere. Birakay faces the common problems in this line of work:  exhaustion; many temptations regarding intoxicating substances and sexual misconduct; stunted emotional growth due to narcissism and ego-sickness; feeling of lack of authenticity.  Birakay is not particularly well-compensated for his work. despite the admiration of many fans, he is the target of frequent criticisms from the Helioptic Authority.
\fs24 \

\fs26 \
